n: 0px 0px; background-repeat: repeat repeat;\">1</a></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 3px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; list-style: none outside none;\"><a class=\"btnPagerCss\" href=\"http://www.bsc.com.vn/WorldMarket.aspx#\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); text-decoration: none; background-image: url(http://www.bsc.com.vn/ESImages/bg_pager.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; border: 1px solid rgb(152, 166, 174); border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; display: block; height: 26px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; width: 25px; background-position: 0px 0px; background-repeat: repeat repeat;\">2&nbsp;</a></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 3px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; list-style: none outside none;\"><a class=\"btnPagerCss\" href=\"http://www.bsc.com.vn/WorldMarket.aspx#\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); text-decoration: none; background-image: url(http://www.bsc.com.vn/ESImages/bg_pager.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; border: 1px solid rgb(152, 166, 174); border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; display: block; height: 26px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; width: 25px; background-position: 0px 0px; background-repeat: repeat repeat;\">3&nbsp;</a></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 3px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; list-style: none outside none;\"><a class=\"btnPagerCss\" href=\"http://www.bsc.com.vn/WorldMarket.aspx#\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); text-decoration: none; background-image: url(http://www.bsc.com.vn/ESImages/bg_pager.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; border: 1px solid rgb(152, 166, 174); border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; display: block; height: 26px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; width: 25px; background-position: 0px 0px; background-repeat: repeat repeat;\">4&nbsp;</a></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 3px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; list-style: none outside none;\"><a class=\"btnPagerCss\" href=\"http://www.bsc.com.vn/WorldMarket.aspx#\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(106, 106, 106); text-decoration: none; background-image: url(http://www.bsc.com.vn/ESImages/bg_pager.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; border: 1px solid rgb(152, 166, 174); border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; display: block; height: 26px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; width: 25px; background-position: 0px 0px; background-repeat: repeat repeat;\">5&nbsp;</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n','file.396418.jpg','2014-05-18',10,1,3,2,'en'),(79,'Where the only rule is \'be cool\'','','<p class=\"introduction\" id=\"story_continues_1\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left; font-weight: bold;\">How did coding get so cool?</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Let&#39;s be honest, it wasn&#39;t always that way. Being able to speak to computers in their own language wasn&#39;t the best way to impress at parties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">But in a world of digital billionaires it has become a deeply fashionable skill. It turns out that it&#39;s the geek who is going to inherit the earth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">And one of the fast-growing coding clubs has been CoderDojo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">It&#39;s a not-for-profit organisation running coding clubs for young people in 38 countries, with the founding principle that the only rule is: &quot;Be cool.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">It is established across Europe and North America, with a few clubs scattered across Asia and South America. Discussions with the US state department could see support for the clubs spreading further into Africa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"cross-head\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; display: block; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 1.231em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Temple of learning</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The clubs are run by volunteers, teaching young people how to write code, build websites and make apps. The club&#39;s start-up supporters have an almost evangelical enthusiasm for these self-taught, unstructured, unbossy events.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The &quot;dojo&quot; is borrowed from Japanese martial arts, as the temple of learning. It taps into a culture where students are expected to pass on what they have learned to others, with the learners becoming mentors.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"caption body-narrow-width\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; position: relative; clear: both; float: right; display: inline; margin: 0px -160px 16px 16px;\"><img alt=\"Bill Liao\" height=\"405\" src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/73412000/jpg/_73412210_billliao.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; -webkit-user-select: none; position: relative; letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: italic;\" width=\"304\" /><span style=\"display: block; width: 304px;\">Bill Liao wants coding to be a sociable activity</span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Behind the CoderDojo project is Bill Liao, an entrepreneur and philanthropist who grew up in Australia and now lives in West Cork in Ireland.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Coding is at the heart of the digital world, he says. If you want to understand this world then you need to understand its language.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;Coding is a language skill.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;The best coders I know are poets. They have creativity and economy of expression. You see great code and it is elegant in its simplicity and rich in meaning.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">We don&#39;t always recognise the beauty of well-made technology, he says, even when it is right in front of us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;We marvel at a two year old tapping at an iPad using a computer. We should really be marvelling at an Apple engineer who can make a computer that a two year old can use.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Another reason for the upsurge in interest in coding is that it is going to help young people in a tough jobs market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;Name a field of endeavour where understanding code wouldn&#39;t benefit your career choice,&quot; says Mr Liao.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"cross-head\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; display: block; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 1.231em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Code father</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Setting up the CoderDojo clubs, he says surprised him by how much children wanted to learn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">And he was pleasantly surprised by how generous people can be in donating their time and premises.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">As an example of how it works on the ground, Rob Curran is a local CoderDojo &quot;champion&quot; in Wilmslow, Cheshire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Mr Curran came across the project when he brought his own son to a dojo and was so impressed that he now helps run a monthly session which attracts between 30 and 90 youngsters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">They learn how to use coding programmes such as Scratch, or use the simple Raspberry Pi computer or experiment with computer game such as Minecraft.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"caption body-width\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; position: relative; clear: both; float: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px;\"><img alt=\"WhatsApp\" height=\"261\" src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/73365000/jpg/_73365495_021215979-1.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; -webkit-user-select: none; position: relative; letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: italic;\" width=\"464\" /><span style=\"display: block; width: 464px;\">Will coders be the next generation of App millionaires?</span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">What is the appeal for youngsters? It gives them hours of uninterrupted computer time and importantly, he says: &quot;It is not school.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">But the rise of computer clubs doesn&#39;t mean that the economy is suddenly awash with youngsters with the right skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Mr Liao&#39;s day job is as a venture capitalist and he says there are too many bright ideas looking for investors which are held back by a lack of coders.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;The entire world is run on code and we have run out of coders,&quot; he says.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">As an entrepreneur, he says he wants to create an environment where youngsters can try to learn these skills and not worry about failure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">When they succeed there is instant playground credibility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">A 12 year old attending a CoderDojo club in Cork made a games app that was accepted for Apple&#39;s App Store, he says. He was so young his mother had to register the account for him.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Being able to show friends your own app on an iPhone is &quot;achingly cool&quot;, he says.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"cross-head\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; display: block; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 1.231em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">&#39;Hated school&#39;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">While the parents might be thinking about the cash advantages of a junior Bill Gates in the family, Mr Liao says such coding clubs have got to be sociable, reassuring and spontaneous places.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">What he wants to avoid is the sense of isolation he felt as a child, teaching himself to use a computer in his bedroom in the suburbs of Melbourne.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"caption body-width\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; position: relative; clear: both; float: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px;\"><img alt=\"Introducing coding event\" height=\"261\" src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/73412000/jpg/_73412216_021414905-2.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; -webkit-user-select: none; position: relative; letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: italic;\" width=\"464\" /><span style=\"display: block; width: 464px;\">An introduction to coding event in south London last week</span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;I hated school. Mostly because I was racially vilified as a half-Chinese kid. It was pretty horrible.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">But learning to use a computer was his escape from loneliness and bullying.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;It gave me access to something that has been incredibly powerful throughout my life.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">And he says he has great empathy for the lonely child learning alone, wanting them to feel safe in the CoderDojo set up.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;Learning is a social activity. You learn more when you&#39;re doing it together.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"caption body-narrow-width\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; position: relative; clear: both; float: right; display: inline; margin: 0px -160px 16px 16px;\"><img alt=\"Prince Andrew at CoderDojo event last week\" height=\"405\" src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/73505000/jpg/_73505679_dukeofyork_billliaocoderdojo_hays.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; -webkit-user-select: none; position: relative; letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: italic;\" width=\"304\" /><span style=\"display: block; width: 304px;\">The Duke of York gave a royal seal approval to coding clubs at a CoderDojo event last week</span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">And as the CoderDojo website puts it: &quot;Bullying, lying, wasting people&#39;s time and so on is uncool.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">He is also an advocate of the principle of working many years to become an overnight success. He describes his years refining the CoderDojo idea, with co-founder James Whelton, as his &quot;Beatles in Hamburg years&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">It isn&#39;t just CoderDojo that is surfing the coding wave. There are many other organisations bringing the coding message to young people, such as Code Club and Code Academy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">In the UK, this is the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/www.yearofcode.org\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 113, 148); line-height: 16px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;\">Year of Code</a>, with the aim of encouraging more people to try to learn the language.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">In the US and the UK there are &quot;hour of code&quot; projects for quick-fire lessons, supported by tech giants such as Microsoft and Google.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The BBC&#39;s School Report project has also gathered&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/schoolreport/25967053\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 113, 148); line-height: 16px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;\">resources and materials</a>&nbsp;about learning to code.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">And even though CoderDojo clubs are spreading around the world, Mr Liao won&#39;t be rushing to see them all.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Not because of lack of interest, but because he has given up air-travel as part of an environmental, tree-planting project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">But the idea he wants to plant in all these clubs is to encourage creativity without a fear of failure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;It&#39;s not just free, it&#39;s free thinking. It&#39;s not closed and institutional,&quot; he says.</p>\r\n','doanhnghiep.jpg','2014-05-06',12,1,3,NULL,'en'),(80,'Nhiều doanh nghiệp đặt mục tiêu lợi nhuận cao chót vót','Bên cạnh những đơn vị thận trọng với kết quả kinh doanh 2014, mùa đại hội cổ đông vừa qua cũng ghi nhận nhiều công ty địa ốc, ngân hàng đặt kỳ vọng tăng trưởng 3 con số trong năm nay.','<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Với dự t&iacute;nh lợi nhuận sau thuế hợp nhất 2014 cao hơn 330% so với mức thực hiện 2013 v&agrave; đạt tr&ecirc;n 64 tỷ đồng, C&ocirc;ng ty Ph&aacute;t triển Nh&agrave; Thủ Đức (Thủ Đức House, M&atilde; CK: TDH) đang được xem l&agrave; một trong những doanh nghiệp c&oacute; kế hoạch tăng trưởng l&atilde;i cao nhất năm nay. Mục ti&ecirc;u n&agrave;y vấp phải kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t ho&agrave;i nghi từ ph&iacute;a cổ đ&ocirc;ng khi năm ngo&aacute;i, c&ocirc;ng ty suy giảm doanh thu từ hoạt động đầu tư t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; lỗ 4,4 tỷ đồng trong c&aacute;c đơn vị li&ecirc;n doanh li&ecirc;n kết. Cộng th&ecirc;m chi ph&iacute; l&atilde;i vay, lợi nhuận sau thuế hợp nhất 2013 của Thủ Đức House chỉ đủ ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh 36% kế hoạch năm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">D&ugrave; vậy, l&atilde;nh đạo Thủ Đức House cho rằng kế hoạch kinh doanh năm nay kh&aacute;c v&agrave; khẳng định ban điều h&agrave;nh sẽ nỗ lực đưa c&ocirc;ng ty tăng trưởng. &Ocirc;ng L&ecirc; Ch&iacute; Hiếu &ndash; Tổng gi&aacute;m đốc doanh nghiệp chia sẻ lĩnh vực ch&iacute;nh Thủ Đức House hướng đến vẫn l&agrave; bất động sản, xuất nhập khẩu v&agrave; x&acirc;y dựng hạ tầng kỹ thuật. Dự kiến doanh thu từ địa ốc v&agrave; xuất nhập khẩu sẽ chiếm tỷ trọng nhiều nhất với lần lượt 56-32%.</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tplCaption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; width: 480px;\">\r\n	<tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n			<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;\"><img alt=\"PDR-2174-1399347278.jpg\" data-pwidth=\"480\" data-width=\"488\" src=\"http://m.f25.img.vnecdn.net/2014/05/06/PDR-2174-1399347278.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; max-width: 100%; width: 480px;\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n			<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;\">\r\n			<p class=\"Image\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; line-height: normal; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);\">Năm nay C&ocirc;ng ty Ph&aacute;t triển Bất động sản Ph&aacute;t Đạt dự t&iacute;nh thu l&atilde;i cao tr&ecirc;n chục lần so với 2013. Ảnh: PDR</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Ngo&agrave;i Thủ Đức House, một đơn vị kh&aacute;c cũng trong lĩnh vực địa ốc đặt mục ti&ecirc;u lợi nhuận cao ch&oacute;t v&oacute;t l&agrave; C&ocirc;ng ty cổ phần Ph&aacute;t triển Bất động sản Ph&aacute;t Đạt (M&atilde; CK: PDR). Năm nay doanh nghiệp của người gi&agrave;u thứ 9 tr&ecirc;n s&agrave;n chứng kho&aacute;n &ndash; &ocirc;ng Nguyễn Văn Đạt dự kiến thu về 50,4 tỷ đồng lợi nhuận trước thuế, cao gấp 13 lần so với mức thực hiện 2013.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Kế hoạch n&agrave;y cũng lại gặp kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t nghi ngại từ ph&iacute;a cổ đ&ocirc;ng khi cuối năm ngo&aacute;i, Bất động sản Ph&aacute;t Đạt c&ograve;n xin giảm chỉ ti&ecirc;u lợi nhuận trước thuế xuống 12 lần so với mức từng đề ra hồi đầu năm. Tại đại hội thường ni&ecirc;n vừa tổ chức hồi th&aacute;ng Tư, &ocirc;ng Nguyễn Văn Đạt &ndash; Chủ tịch doanh nghiệp đ&atilde; trấn an c&aacute;c cổ đ&ocirc;ng v&agrave; khẳng định kế hoạch 2014 l&agrave; khả thi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">&ldquo;Do t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh thị trường bất động sản đ&atilde; c&oacute; c&aacute;c dấu hiệu tốt l&ecirc;n nhiều v&agrave; thủ tục dự &aacute;n chủ đạo của c&ocirc;ng ty l&agrave; The Everrich 3 sắp ho&agrave;n tất để b&aacute;n c&aacute;c villa, khả năng đạt kế hoạch năm nay l&agrave; rất cao. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i tin tưởng sẽ kh&ocirc;ng điều chỉnh kế hoạch. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, t&ugrave;y t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh thực tế, HĐQT sẽ quyết định&rdquo;, &ocirc;ng Đạt chia sẻ với cổ đ&ocirc;ng trong đại hội.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Trao đổi với<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;VnExpress</em>, &ocirc;ng V&otilde; Tấn Th&agrave;nh &ndash; Ph&oacute; tổng gi&aacute;m đốc Đầu tư của Bất động sản Ph&aacute;t Đạt cho biết th&ecirc;m &ldquo;qu&yacute; III c&ocirc;ng ty sẽ c&oacute; doanh thu v&agrave; tạo lợi nhuận từ dự &aacute;n Everrich 3&rdquo;. Vị n&agrave;y cũng cho hay hiện thời chỉ c&ograve;n 1-2 thủ tục dứt điểm l&agrave; c&oacute; thể triển khai b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng. Ri&ecirc;ng tiền đất nền c&oacute; thể thu xong hết trong năm nay, c&ograve;n tiền nh&agrave; phải k&eacute;o d&agrave;i sang năm tới.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Qu&yacute; I vừa qua, kết quả kinh doanh của Bất động sản Ph&aacute;t Đạt chưa thực sự khả quan khi l&atilde;i sau thuế chỉ 235 triệu đồng, chủ yếu nhờ thu nhập từ c&aacute;c khoản tiền phạt hợp đồng nhận được. Trước đ&oacute;, ba th&aacute;ng đầu năm c&ocirc;ng ty thu về 19 tỷ đồng doanh thu nhưng gi&aacute; vốn h&agrave;ng b&aacute;n qu&aacute; cao (tr&ecirc;n 13 tỷ đồng) đ&atilde; khiến lợi nhuận giảm mạnh. Tại ng&agrave;y 31/3, vốn chủ sở hữu của Bất động sản Ph&aacute;t Đạt tr&ecirc;n 1.427 tỷ đồng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Kh&ocirc;ng chỉ doanh nghiệp bất động sản, một số đơn vị kh&aacute;c trong lĩnh vực sản xuất hay ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng cũng li&ecirc;n tục tr&igrave;nh cổ đ&ocirc;ng mục ti&ecirc;u l&atilde;i năm nay cao tr&ecirc;n 100% so với năm ngo&aacute;i. Trong số n&agrave;y, HĐQT Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng An B&igrave;nh (ABBank) dự kiến l&atilde;i trước thuế 2014 tăng 110%, đạt 400 tỷ đồng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Năm ngo&aacute;i, tổng lợi nhuận trước thuế của ABBank l&agrave; 191 tỷ đồng, giảm 61% so với năm 2012 v&agrave; chỉ ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh 29% kế hoạch. Với kết quả n&agrave;y, nh&agrave; băng chỉ c&oacute; thể trả cổ tức l&agrave; 246 đồng tr&ecirc;n mỗi cổ phiếu v&agrave; từng khiến nhiều cổ đ&ocirc;ng tỏ th&aacute;i độ thất vọng trong đại hội cổ đ&ocirc;ng vừa tổ chức gần đ&acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">C&ograve;n tại Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng cổ phần Quốc d&acirc;n, lợi nhuận trước thuế 2014 cũng được HĐQT dự kiến tăng 402,6% so với năm ngo&aacute;i, đạt 96,3 tỷ đồng. Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng cổ phần Ph&aacute;t triển Mekong (MDBank) cũng đặt mục ti&ecirc;u l&atilde;i cao hơn 202%, l&ecirc;n 222 tỷ đồng. Ph&iacute;a doanh nghiệp sản xuất-thương mại, C&ocirc;ng ty cổ phần Xuất nhập khẩu Thủy sản An Giang kỳ vọng tăng l&atilde;i trước thuế năm nay 224% (l&ecirc;n 120 tỷ đồng).</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Trao đổi với<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;VnExpress</em>, &ocirc;ng Tống Minh Tuấn &ndash; Gi&aacute;m đốc Khối Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Đầu tư tại C&ocirc;ng ty Chứng kho&aacute;n Vietcombank (VCBS) cho rằng việc đặt mục ti&ecirc;u lợi nhuận cao c&oacute; thể chỉ nhằm mục đ&iacute;ch ngắn hạn như tăng vốn, ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh th&ecirc;m cổ phần. Đối với cổ đ&ocirc;ng, động th&aacute;i n&agrave;y cũng c&oacute; thể củng cố th&ecirc;m tiềm năng, triển vọng của cổ phiếu do ch&iacute;nh c&ocirc;ng ty ni&ecirc;m yết, &ocirc;ng Tuấn chia sẻ.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Cũng chung quan điểm tr&ecirc;n, &ocirc;ng Phan Dũng Kh&aacute;nh &ndash; Gi&aacute;m đốc Tư vấn đầu tư, C&ocirc;ng ty Chứng kho&aacute;n MayBank Kim Eng (MBKE) nhận định th&ecirc;m một trong những yếu tố lớn nhất để c&aacute;c doanh nghiệp đưa ra mức chỉ ti&ecirc;u cao như vậy l&agrave; họ hầu như đ&atilde; t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n xong đầu ra.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">&ldquo;Thật sự m&igrave;nh l&agrave; người ngo&agrave;i th&igrave; c&oacute; thể chưa thấy r&otilde; nội bộ c&ocirc;ng ty. C&oacute; thể họ đ&atilde; t&igrave;m xong đối t&aacute;c chiến lược hay người mua để bảo đảm sẽ thu l&atilde;i khi b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng, dịch vụ. Những thương vụ n&agrave;y đa phần chỉ người trong doanh nghiệp nắm trước, về nguy&ecirc;n tắc l&agrave; phải c&ocirc;ng khai nhưng c&oacute; thể chưa đến thời điểm ban l&atilde;nh đạo muốn c&ocirc;ng bố&rdquo;, chuy&ecirc;n gia MBKE giải th&iacute;ch th&ecirc;m.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">D&ugrave; vậy, &ocirc;ng Kh&aacute;nh cho rằng chỉ ti&ecirc;u lợi nhuận ch&oacute;t v&oacute;t vẫn chưa đủ thuyết phục để khẳng định sức khỏe cũng như độ bền vững hoạt động của c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty. Bản th&acirc;n nh&agrave; đầu tư phải tỉnh t&aacute;o v&agrave; l&agrave;m chủ t&igrave;nh thế bằng c&aacute;ch lu&ocirc;n đặt c&acirc;u hỏi đến doanh nghiệp về việc triển khai hoạt động, đồng thời kiểm tra t&iacute;nh hợp l&yacute; trong c&aacute;c c&acirc;u trả lời.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Theo chuy&ecirc;n gia n&agrave;y, kh&ocirc;ng loại trừ trường hợp tung chỉ ti&ecirc;u kinh doanh &ldquo;khủng&rdquo; l&agrave; biện ph&aacute;p quảng b&aacute; đỡ tốn chi ph&iacute; nhất cho doanh nghiệp. &ldquo;Trong bối cảnh ai cũng đặt chỉ ti&ecirc;u lợi nhuận thấp, ri&ecirc;ng những c&ocirc;ng ty n&agrave;y lại nhắm mức cao hẳn n&ecirc;n sẽ thu h&uacute;t nh&agrave; đầu tư, tạo tiếng vang. Ngay cả những dự &aacute;n đang triển khai cũng được quảng b&aacute; khiến nhiều người biết đến&rdquo;, &ocirc;ng Kh&aacute;nh chia sẻ.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Trong ba th&aacute;ng đầu năm, đa phần c&aacute;c doanh nghiệp tr&ecirc;n vẫn chưa c&ocirc;ng bố kết quả kinh doanh. Ngo&agrave;i Bất động sản Ph&aacute;t Đạt, chỉ mới c&oacute; Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Quốc D&acirc;n c&ocirc;ng bố b&aacute;o c&aacute;o ri&ecirc;ng lẻ qu&yacute; I nhưng lợi nhuận trước thuế chỉ bằng hơn 3% so với mục ti&ecirc;u đề ra, tương đương tr&ecirc;n 3 tỷ đồng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">&Ocirc;ng Kh&aacute;nh khuyến nghị c&aacute;c cổ đ&ocirc;ng, nh&agrave; đầu tư vẫn n&ecirc;n l&agrave; người chủ động nhất đến hoạt động c&ocirc;ng ty bằng c&aacute;ch thường xuy&ecirc;n trao đổi với đại diện doanh nghiệp. C&ograve;n nếu kh&ocirc;ng ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh kế hoạch, c&aacute;c đơn vị n&agrave;y vẫn c&oacute; đường lui th&ocirc;ng qua việc xin giảm mục ti&ecirc;u lợi nhuận. Theo chuy&ecirc;n gia VCBS - &ocirc;ng Tống Minh Tuấn, phần lớn những trường hợp như vậy, cổ đ&ocirc;ng l&agrave; người chịu thiệt nhiều nhất.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Cuối năm ngo&aacute;i, h&agrave;ng loạt doanh nghiệp đ&atilde; li&ecirc;n tục xin cổ đ&ocirc;ng giảm mục ti&ecirc;u l&atilde;i từ 15% đến hơn 20%. Sang những th&aacute;ng đầu năm 2014, đa phần c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty đều rụt r&egrave; với kế hoạch lợi nhuận năm. Nhiều đơn vị c&oacute; quy m&ocirc; vốn cả ngh&igrave;n tỷ đồng năm nay lại chỉ d&aacute;m đặt tăng trưởng doanh thu trong khi tr&igrave;nh cổ đ&ocirc;ng mục ti&ecirc;u lợi nhuận thấp hơn so với 2013.</p>\r\n','dn.jpg','2014-05-11',10,1,2,6,'vi'),(81,'56 ngày trốn trên trần bếp trại giam','Lợi dụng sơ hở lúc lao động, Phước “Gà” kẻ đang thụ án chung thân, trốn biệt tăm trong bếp ăn của trại giam gần hai tháng.','<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Huỳnh Văn Phước (Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo;, 51 tuổi, ở th&agrave;nh phố Nha Trang, tỉnh Kh&aacute;nh Ho&agrave;) l&agrave; tay giang hồ cộm c&aacute;n, từng c&oacute; 3 tiền &aacute;n v&agrave; nhiều lần trốn khỏi trại giam. Sau thời gian d&agrave;i thụ &aacute;n, năm 2004, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; về với cuộc sống tự do, kiếm kế sinh nhai ở ga Nha Trang.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Kh&ocirc;ng ch&iacute; th&uacute; l&agrave;m ăn, g&atilde; thường xuy&ecirc;n đ&aacute;nh bạc với những người khu&acirc;n v&aacute;c tại ga Nha Trang. Đ&ecirc;m 18/4/2008, Phước thua bạc n&ecirc;n tức tối khi thấy bạn chơi đứng dậy, từ chối chơi tiếp. Phước g&acirc;y hấn, to tiếng với anh Nguyễn Thanh Tuấn, người thắng bạc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Thấy anh trai c&atilde;i cọ với Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo;, anh Nguyễn Thanh Kiệt ra can ngăn. Cho rằng, anh Tuấn gọi th&ecirc;m người đ&aacute;nh m&igrave;nh, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; r&uacute;t dao đ&acirc;m cả hai anh em họ. Trong l&uacute;c anh Tuấn may mắn tho&aacute;t chết, anh Kiệt đ&atilde; tử vong do mất m&aacute;u cấp. G&acirc;y &aacute;n xong, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; bỏ trốn v&agrave; một tuần sau bị bắt. C&ugrave;ng năm đ&oacute;, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; bị TAND tỉnh Kh&aacute;nh Ho&agrave; tuy&ecirc;n phạt chung th&acirc;n tội Giết người v&agrave; Cố &yacute; g&acirc;y thương t&iacute;ch.</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tplCaption\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; width: 480px;\">\r\n	<tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n			<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;\"><img alt=\"pham-nhan-6779-1399166678.jpg\" data-natural-=\"\" data-pwidth=\"480\" data-width=\"500\" src=\"http://m.f29.img.vnecdn.net/2014/05/04/pham-nhan-6779-1399166678.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; max-width: 100%; width: 480px;\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n			<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;\">\r\n			<p class=\"Image\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; line-height: normal; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Một buổi lao động tại nh&agrave; ăn trong ph&acirc;n trại 1 trại giam Ph&uacute; Sơn. Ảnh:&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Việt Dũng</em>.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Đầu th&aacute;ng 12/2010, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; được thuy&ecirc;n chuyển về từ miền Nam ra trại giam Ph&uacute; Sơn - Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n thụ &aacute;n. Thời gian đầu, g&atilde; tỏ ra hiền l&agrave;nh, chấp h&agrave;nh đầy đủ nội quy của trại giam. Theo một c&aacute;n bộ trại Ph&uacute; Sơn, do Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; l&agrave; một kẻ giang hồ cộm c&aacute;n, c&oacute; 3 tiền &aacute;n n&ecirc;n hắn lu&ocirc;n được quản l&yacute; chặt chẽ. Hơn một năm thụ &aacute;n tại trại, một ng&agrave;y lợi dụng sơ hở, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; biến mất.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Lệnh truy n&atilde; với Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; được lực lượng chức năng ph&aacute;t đi to&agrave;n quốc. Tổ c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c trại giam c&ugrave;ng với c&ocirc;ng an tỉnh Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n, Tổng Cục 8 phối hợp truy bắt tù nh&acirc;n nguy hiểm n&agrave;y. Theo nhận định của cơ quan chức năng, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; từng c&oacute; hai lần vượt ngục v&agrave;o c&aacute;c năm 1991, 1995 n&ecirc;n t&ecirc;n n&agrave;y c&oacute; nhiều &ldquo;kinh nghiệm&rdquo; lẩn trốn. Mỗi lần vượt ngục, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; lại c&oacute; th&ecirc;m t&igrave;nh nh&acirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">H&agrave;ng chục trinh s&aacute;t, chia th&agrave;nh nhiều mũi toả đi khắp c&aacute;c nơi, r&agrave; so&aacute;t mối quan hệ của t&ecirc;n n&agrave;y song hắn vẫn mất dạng. Đ&atilde; c&oacute; l&uacute;c, c&aacute;c trinh s&aacute;t tưởng chừng Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; chui xuống đất v&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n dấu vết. &ldquo;Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cử một tổ 5-6 người, chốt chặn ở ga Qu&aacute;n Triều để l&ugrave;ng bắt Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo;, một c&aacute;n bộ trại giam Ph&uacute; Sơn cho biết. L&uacute;c đ&oacute;, c&aacute;c anh nhận định, Phước c&oacute; nghề khu&acirc;n v&aacute;c n&ecirc;n sẽ tr&agrave; trộn để ấn nấp trong nh&oacute;m c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n. Ngo&agrave;i ra, ở những nơi Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; từng đến, c&aacute;c tổ c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c cũng c&oacute; mặt, r&agrave; so&aacute;t, mai phục. Hơn một th&aacute;ng biến mất, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; vẫn bặt v&ocirc; &acirc;m t&iacute;n. Lực lượng chức năng tập trung quyết liệt nh&acirc;n sự truy t&igrave;m t&ecirc;n n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Giữa l&uacute;c đ&oacute;, Bộ C&ocirc;ng an tổ chức Hội thảo an to&agrave;n vệ sinh thực phẩm v&agrave; trại giam Ph&uacute; Sơn l&agrave; đơn vị diễn ra sự kiện n&agrave;y. Trong l&uacute;c dọn dẹp ở khu bếp ăn của trại giam để đo&agrave;n c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c kiểm tra, đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute;, c&aacute;n bộ ph&aacute;t hiện trần bếp c&oacute; vết cậy v&agrave; nhiều vỏ m&igrave; t&ocirc;m. &ldquo;Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&ograve;n tưởng l&agrave; chuột tha giấy m&igrave; t&ocirc;m l&ecirc;n đ&oacute; nhưng kh&aacute; bất ngờ, kẻ mang &aacute;n chung th&acirc;n Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; m&agrave; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i truy t&igrave;m lại đang ẩn n&aacute;u tr&ecirc;n trần g&aacute;c bếp&rdquo;, một c&aacute;n bộ trại giam cho biết sau khi bắt lại Phước.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Sau 56 ng&agrave;y trốn, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; vẫn l&agrave;nh lặn, b&eacute;o tốt v&agrave; sạch sẽ. Hắn khai, sau khi rời khỏi nh&oacute;m phạm nh&acirc;n trong tổ lao động, đ&atilde; trốn l&ecirc;n g&aacute;c bếp. G&atilde; ở tr&ecirc;n đ&oacute; cả ng&agrave;y, chịu c&aacute;i n&oacute;ng m&ugrave;a h&egrave; dội xuống. Đợi đến đ&ecirc;m tối, hắn tr&egrave;o xuống bếp, lục lọi đồ ăn v&agrave; tắm rửa b&igrave;nh thường. Những lần d&agrave;i ng&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng rời được khỏi nơi ẩn nấp, hắn ăn m&igrave; t&ocirc;m được t&iacute;ch trữ lấy từ khu bếp. Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; thừa nhận trong những t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n, g&atilde; qu&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng vứt bỏ giấy m&igrave; t&ocirc;m. Việc lẩn trốn ở tr&ecirc;n g&aacute;c bếp, hắn bảo đợi cơ hội ra ngo&agrave;i, song &ocirc;ng ta cũng thừa nhận &ldquo;kh&oacute; c&oacute; khả năng&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Với tội Trốn khỏi nơi giam giữ, Phước &ldquo;G&agrave;&rdquo; bị TAND huyện Ph&uacute; Lương (Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n) tuy&ecirc;n phạt 4 năm, tổng hợp &aacute;n cũ &ocirc;ng ta phải chấp h&agrave;nh t&ugrave; chung th&acirc;n.</p>\r\n','pl.jpg','2014-05-18',10,1,2,4,'vi'),(82,'Hillary Clinton warns US to \'rein in\' gun culture','Hillary Clinton has said US gun culture has become \"way out of balance\" and attacked the notion that \"anybody can have a gun, anywhere, anytime\".','<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;I don&#39;t believe that is in the best interest of the vast majority,&quot; said the former secretary of state.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">That belief does not conflict with the rights of people to own guns, she told a conference in Maryland.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Mrs Clinton is widely expected to enter the race to be Democratic presidential candidate for the 2016 election.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Speaking at the National Council for Behavioral Health conference in Oxon Hill, Maryland, on Tuesday, she pointed to recent shootings that involved teenagers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;I think again we&#39;re way out of balance. I think that we&#39;ve got to rein in what has become an almost article of faith that anybody can have a gun anywhere, anytime,&#39;&#39; Clinton said.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">That&#39;s not in the majority&#39;s best interests, she added. &quot;And I think you can say that and still support the right of people to own guns.&#39;&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">After a mass shooting at a school in Newtown, Connecticut, in which 20 children and six school staff members were killed, the Obama administration tried to tighten up gun laws.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">But the Democratic-controlled Senate voted against legislation pushed by the president that would have expanded background checks for firearm purchases to gun shows and online sales.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"cross-head\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; display: block; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 1.231em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Tight-lipped</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">If Clinton runs for president, her views on gun control would clash with many Republicans, who have largely opposed efforts to tighten gun laws.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">She warned that having so many people with fully licensed firearms on them in places like cinemas meant it more likely that shootings would happen over mundane issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">In January a man was killed and his wife hurt after a shooting that arose from a dispute over the use of a mobile phone in a Florida cinema.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Mrs Clinton has refused to be drawn on whether she will run in 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">She told the conference she was still considering her future. &quot;Stay tuned,&#39;&#39; she added.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The former secretary of state also made no mention of Monica Lewinsky, who on Tuesday broke her silence about her affair with Mrs Clinton&#39;s husband, Bill Clinton, when he was president.</p>\r\n','tg.jpg','2014-05-18',10,1,2,NULL,'en'),(83,'Có được lái xe khi bị tạm giữ bằng?','Tôi bị phạt vì rẽ không xi nhan và bị tạm giữ giấy phép lái xe. Xin hỏi giấy hẹn đến giải quyết tại Phòng cảnh sát giao thông có thay thế được bằng lái trong thời gian này hay không?','<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">T&ocirc;i bị cảnh s&aacute;t giao th&ocirc;ng lập bi&ecirc;n bản, phạt vi phạm v&igrave; điều khiển xe m&aacute;y rẽ phải kh&ocirc;ng xi nhan. Cảnh s&aacute;t đ&atilde; tạm giữ giấy ph&eacute;p l&aacute;i xe, viết bi&ecirc;n bản vi phạm h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; hẹn t&ocirc;i đến Ph&ograve;ng Cảnh s&aacute;t giao th&ocirc;ng để giải quyết.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; font-size: 14px;\">Xin hỏi, t&ocirc;i bị phạt c&oacute; đ&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng? Trong khi chờ giải quyết, t&ocirc;i c&oacute; thể tham gia giao th&ocirc;ng b&igrave;nh thường kh&ocirc;ng? Giấy hẹn c&oacute; gi&aacute; trị thay thế những giấy tờ m&agrave; t&ocirc;i đang bị tạm giữ hay kh&ocirc;ng?</p>\r\n','bằng lái.jpg','2014-05-20',10,1,3,3,'vi'),(84,'Stars boycott Beverly Hills Hotel over Brunei \'sharia\' law','Stars of Hollywood are boycotting one of the area\'s most famous hotels because of a harsh Islamic penal code introduced by Brunei\'s government.','<h1 class=\"story-header\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 34px; margin: 3px -160px 13px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.461em; clear: both; position: relative; width: 623px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: -1px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"caption full-width\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; position: relative; clear: both; float: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px;\"><img alt=\"People protest outside the Beverly Hills Hotel, which is owned by the Sultan of Brunei, over Brunei\'s strict sharia law penal code in Beverly Hills, California 5 May 2014\" height=\"351\" src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/74679000/jpg/_74679527_74679526.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; -webkit-user-select: none; position: relative; letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: italic;\" width=\"624\" /><span style=\"display: block; width: 624px;\">Demonstrators protest over Brunei&#39;s new harsh Islamic penal code at the Beverly Hills Hotel</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"story-feature related narrow\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; position: relative; margin: 0px -160px 16px 16px; width: 144px; float: right; display: inline; overflow: hidden; clear: right;\"><a class=\"hidden\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-27303085#story_continues_1\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 113, 148); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; position: absolute; top: -5000px; left: -5000px;\">Continue reading the main story</a>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 11px 0px 12px; font-size: 1.231em; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(216, 216, 216); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(216, 216, 216); font-weight: bold; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Related Stories</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"related-links-list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding-top: 8px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both; border-top-style: none;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; text-rendering: auto; position: relative; background-image: none;\"><a class=\"story\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27216798\" rel=\"published-1398838336760\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 113, 148); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;\">Brunei introduces tough Islamic law</a></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; text-rendering: auto; position: relative; background-image: none;\"><a class=\"story\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-pacific-12990058\" rel=\"published-1302100163555\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 113, 148); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;\">Brunei profile</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"introduction\" id=\"story_continues_1\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left; font-weight: bold;\">Stars of Hollywood are boycotting one of the area&#39;s most famous hotels because of a harsh Islamic penal code introduced by Brunei&#39;s government.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Comedians Jay Leno and Ellen DeGeneres are among the celebrities supporting the boycott against the Beverly Hills Hotel and other hotels owned by Brunei.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">After a heated debate, the city council unanimously voted to condemn Brunei.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Brunei&#39;s leader, Sultan Hassanal Bolkiah, announced the first phase of the new penalties last week.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"story-feature wide \" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; position: relative; margin: 0px -160px 16px 16px; width: 304px; float: right; display: inline; overflow: hidden; clear: right;\"><a class=\"hidden\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-27303085#story_continues_2\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 113, 148); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; position: absolute; top: -5000px; left: -5000px;\">Continue reading the main story</a>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 11px 0px 12px; font-size: 1.231em; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(216, 216, 216); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(216, 216, 216); font-weight: bold; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Analysis</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"position: relative; padding: 1px 0px 16px; border: none; margin: 0px; clear: both; overflow: hidden;\"><span class=\"byline-picture\" style=\"display: inline; margin: 0px; float: left; padding-top: 2px;\"><img alt=\"image of Regan Morris\" src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/66716000/jpg/_66716886_photo.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; -webkit-user-select: none; display: block; margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; position: relative; top: 0px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: italic;\" /></span><span class=\"byline-name\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0px; font-size: 1.231em; font-weight: bold; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; padding-bottom: 2px; border: none;\">Regan Morris</span><span class=\"byline-title\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0px;\">BBC News, Los Angeles</span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The Beverly Hills Hotel is so ingrained in Hollywood culture that it&#39;s hard to imagine it without the stars.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The hotel bar, the Polo Lounge, is one of the best places in town to spot celebrities. The pink hotel opened in 1912 and has a storied history - Elizabeth Taylor lived there as a child and also as an adult with Richard Burton.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Aviator Howard Hughes resided on and off for about 30 years and more recently you could bump into Tom Cruise or Ozzy Osbourne in the lobby.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">But now the Motion Picture &amp; Television Fund and the International Women Media Foundation have said they plan to find another venue for their glitzy events. While that will hurt business at the hotel, what remains to be seen is if its celebrity clientele will also take their business elsewhere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">So far, this boycott only involves a handful of celebrities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"story_continues_2\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">They will eventually include death by stoning for homosexuality and adultery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The mayor of Beverly Hills, Lili Bosse, had urged the city council to adopt a resolution condemning Brunei&#39;s new laws and force the country to sell the hotel and others it owns through the Dorchester Collection chain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The council unanimously passed a resolution condemning the sultanate but the meeting was divided on whether to boycott the hotel. Many disagreed with Mayor Bosse&#39;s decision to no longer attend functions there.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Earlier, Virgin group founder Richard Branson<a href=\"https://twitter.com/richardbranson/status/462623689599881217\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 113, 148); line-height: 16px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;\">tweeted on Saturday</a>&nbsp;his employees and family would not stay at the luxury hotel chain &quot;until the Sultan abides by basic human rights&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Several organisations have cancelled events at the hotel, long a gathering place for Hollywood celebrities, including the Motion Picture &amp; Television Fund&#39;s annual Night Before the Oscars charity event and the Feminist Majority Foundation&#39;s annual Global Women&#39;s Rights Awards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">During a small protest in front of the hotel on Monday, Mr Leno said: &quot;I&#39;d like to think that all people are basically good and when they realise this is going on, hopefully they&#39;ll do something about it.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">But Christopher Cowdray, the chief executive of the Dorchester Collection chain, said those protesting have ignored local hotels owned by countries with poor human rights records.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">&quot;There are other hotel companies in this city that are owned by Saudi Arabia... you know, your shirt probably comes from a country which has human rights issues,&quot; Mr Cowdray said, adding a boycott would hurt local employees the most.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"caption full-width\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; position: relative; clear: both; float: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px;\"><img alt=\"Jay Leno speaks at a gathering of Women\'s Rights and LGBT groups protesting across from the Beverly Hills Hotel, 5 May 2014\" height=\"351\" src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/74679000/jpg/_74679649_74679644.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; -webkit-user-select: none; position: relative; letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: italic;\" width=\"624\" /><span style=\"display: block; width: 624px;\">Jay Leno speaks at the protest across from the Beverly Hills Hotel</span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The US government has been largely quiet on the change to Brunei&#39;s penal code, but the state department said on Tuesday it had privately relayed concerns to the Brunei government.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The initial phase of the new penal code introduces fines or prison terms for offences including indecent behaviour, failure to attend Friday prayers and pregnancies out-of-wedlock.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The second phase due to start later this year will cover crimes such as theft and robbery and will involve more stringent penalties such as amputations and flogging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The most severe punishments, such as death by stoning for offences including sodomy and adultery, will be introduced late next year</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Brunei officials have previously said that judges would be given discretion in sentencing. It is not clear to what extent the code will apply to non-Muslims.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">The tiny state, on the island of Borneo has grown rich on oil and gas exports.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helmet, Freesans, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.077em; text-rendering: auto; clear: left;\">Almost three-quarters of those who live there are Malay Muslims, but there are sizeable Buddhist and Christian communities.</p>\r\n','file.396407.jpg','2014-05-15',10,1,3,NULL,'en'),(85,'Chiêm ngưỡng iPhone 5 mạ vàng phiên bản rắn','Chiếc điện thoại mới nhất của Apple mạ vàng đính kim cương nhân tạo, phía sau có hình rắn đúc để đón Tết Qúy Tỵ vừa xuất hiện tại TP HCM. Bên cạnh phiên bản rắn, còn có thêm phiên bản rồng.','<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tplCaption\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-family: arial, tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.97em;\">\r\n	<tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em;\">\r\n		<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em;\">\r\n			<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://l.f5.img.vnexpress.net/2013/01/31/ran-jpg-1359585954-1359586003_500x0.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em; width: 500px; height: 422px;\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em;\">\r\n			<td class=\"Image\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Chiếc điện thoại n&agrave;y được đặt l&agrave;m theo y&ecirc;u cầu đến đ&oacute;n Tết.</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tplCaption\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-family: arial, tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.97em;\">\r\n	<tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em;\">\r\n		<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em;\">\r\n			<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 0.97em;\"><img alt=\"\